This is a placeholder for the raylib static library.

To build raylib for Windows MSVC:
1. Download raylib source from https://github.com/raysan5/raylib
2. Open raylib.sln in Visual Studio
3. Build Release/x64 configuration
4. Copy raylib.lib to this directory

Or use CMake:
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -G "Visual Studio 17 2022" -A x64 ..
cmake --build . --config Release
copy Release\raylib.lib ..
